description: <p>Vidaloka is a Didone display \
  typeface for headlines and short blocks of \
  text. Because of its high contrast it will \
  work best from 16px and above.</p> \
  <p>The main features are curlified drops \
  and sloped terminals. Tail of Q has a \
  distinctive baroque inspired form.</p> \
  <p>Vidaloka is designed by Alexei \
  Vanyashin and Olga Karpushina.</p>

